random small scale twitter stuff

are_you_popular - my first test of twitter api, don't bother even looking at it
cheese - an analysis of the use of cheese on twitter
hose_utils - some random utilities for handling the garden hose data
statuslurp - simple randomish status slurper to augment gardenhose
searchslurp - utils for picking a term, like hadoop, and fire and forget collecting search results (without using streaming api)


